---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main class="about-container">
    <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
    
    <section class="content-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">My Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="content-block">
        <p>
          Data science is not just about algorithms and models—it's about understanding uncertainty, 
          making informed decisions, and continuously updating our beliefs as new evidence arrives.
        </p>
        <p>
          I approach every problem with a Bayesian mindset: start with prior knowledge, observe the data, 
          and update accordingly. This philosophy extends beyond machine learning into how I think about 
          complex systems, decision-making, and life itself.
        </p>
        <p>
          The goal isn't to eliminate uncertainty, but to become comfortable dancing with it. Every model 
          is a simplification, every prediction carries uncertainty, and that's not a bug—it's a feature 
          of reality.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3 class="category-title">Machine Learning</h3>
          <ul class="skill-list">
            <li>Deep Learning (TensorFlow, PyTorch)</li>
            <li>Bayesian Methods</li>
            <li>Time Series Analysis</li>
            <li>Reinforcement Learning</li>
            <li>NLP & Transformers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3 class="category-title">Data Engineering</h3>
          <ul class="skill-list">
            <li>Python, SQL</li>
            <li>Apache Kafka, Spark</li>
            <li>Data Pipelines</li>
            <li>Cloud Infrastructure (AWS, GCP)</li>
            <li>MLOps & Model Deployment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3 class="category-title">Visualization & Tools</h3>
          <ul class="skill-list">
            <li>Plotly.js, D3.js</li>
            <li>Statistical Analysis</li>
            <li>Jupyter, Notebooks</li>
            <li>Version Control (Git)</li>
            <li>Agile Methodologies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .content-block {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .content-block p {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .content-block p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .skill-category {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skill-category:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border-color: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .category-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .skill-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .skill-list li {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .skill-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .skill-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.6);
    font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .skills-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>

